              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer4294252052212664136">Behar did an amazing job at depicting what justice is and what drives certain injustices to occur. I respect the perspective he took on trying to explain that, at the end of the day, we all have the same fears and ambitions and it is only through seeing our similarities with others, rather than our differences, that we can move towards a more peaceful world.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


